channel.title: RuneIxz 508
channel.description:
[center] [img]http://dl.dropbox.com/u/18329363/runeixzbanner.png[/img] hey everybody! As you know i have released my current project OptimusScape. I hit up my good friend RuneWings317, we decided to start a project and combine are names together, i know it doesnt sound like a cool name but lol. Alright this base is a 508 and we just started repacking, but i felt like making the thread. The base is a bulby source and yeah. We are using Tinyscape's client because it is awesome :) here is some media and some goals that we plan to get done. The Team - Kronixz RuneWings317 Questions? Are you planning on hosting? A: no, not at the moment we are not planning to host, just release, but our minds may change Green - Done Orange - Started Red - Not Done Update Log:
Got the new source & client! Thanks tinyscape for the client <3 :D Repacking Source Cleaning Up The Source Updating Networking to NIO Got source working with eclipse, also fixed up the source and now 0 errors
NPCs- Runewings and I have discussed this and we decided that having alot of monsters/bosses are a good thing to have because it does improve the economy. It also keeps players playing and doing stuff so they are not bored. Our goal is to have alot of Training area's and boss spots etc. Our Boss spots will be never before seen before, and with a cool interface hopefully :D Also want to try to have most of the NPC's to have the correct anims ;) Items - Well, just not really much to say about items, but with items all the good items will not be available in shops. They can be obtained from bosses, minigames, and other fun stuff to do around Runeixz Minigames - Well like i was trying to do in my previous project was to make up my own custom minigame and release in tutorial section. I havent thought of anything spotanious at the moment, so im a little stuck. If anyone would recommend anything that would be cool. Back on track, Well we defianetly want to rewrite some minigames as they are buggy and unstable. Skills - as seen in the picture, the biggest skill i want to work on is construction and fishing. With fishing my goal is to add alot of fun places to fish and try to recreate a little thing like runescape i always like to do. I always liked fishing for shrimps by the willows :) Also, i want fishing spots in karamja etc. I think jon and I will continue an idea we had with RuneReverse. The skill is called Brewing, I already made the skillcapes ETC, we just have to start making the actual skill. Cleaning - Jon ofc likes spending time cleaning out alot of files and i cant tell you anything about that because that is what he will be doing lol... uhh yeah thats all i can think of for now. Media: [IMG]http://i44.tinypic.com/994fif.png[/img] [IMG]http://i39.tinypic.com/23s21e.png[/img] [IMG]http://i44.tinypic.com/14j3ipf.png[/img] Supporters: Tinyscape - the super ultra baberr K1ng0frs [/center]
